<p><strong>Show notes for Mac Geek Gab Podcast For June 30, 2008</strong></p>
<p>Before heading off on vacation next week, Dave joins John for an all-out Geek fest, discussing what to do about bad RAM, bad hard drives, how to find speed bottlenecks, and more.  Plus, listeners share tips on iSights, batteries, finding files, and a great startup shortcuts printout!</p>
